Class Execution

  • Object
    • Execution

  • public final class Execution
extends Object
    Represents the unfolding execution of a sequence. This is essentially a wrapper around List<ExecutionOutcome>. Stores information in a list of ExecutionOutcome objects, one for each statement in the sequence.
